Tasks:
1. Don't allow the form to be submitted unless is valid.
2. Validate form fields: required fields must have letters and space only [a-zA-Z ].
	2.1 When an error is occured, show it above the form.
	2.2 When an error is occured, highlight the form input (with red color).
3. When the form is valid, the submit button must be enabled.
4. Allow the user to change the quantity of a product. (Quantity can't be lower than 1)
5. Update the price when the quantity is changed.
6. Allow the user to remove an product from the table. (When this happens, the total price should be updated).